    "description": "<p><strong>FRP PRODUCTS CO PTE LTD</strong> was incorporated on 23 July 1970. We have more than 55&nbsp;years of experience and an established Corrosion Protection Specialist&nbsp;Company in the field of Protective Coatings and Lining Application carrying out maintenance projects in the oil/gas, pharmaceutical&nbsp;&amp; petrochemical industry. Today, <strong>FRP PRODUCTS CO PTE LTD </strong>has emerged as one of Singapore's leading Corrosion Protection Specialist with more than 500 experienced employees and a comprehensive range of equipment in operation.</p>\n<p>Our Vision to be one of the best protective coating and lining applicators by delivering superior quality service in the Process and Construction Industries using the safest and most cost effective methods ensuring total customer satisfaction.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
